com.skratchdot.electribe.model.esx
Interface Song

All Known Implementing Classes:
SongImpl
public interface Song

A representation of the model object 'Song'.

The following features are supported:

  • Name
  • Tempo
  • Tempo Lock
  • Song Length
  • Mute Hold
  • Next Song Number
  • Number Of Song Events Current
  • Number Of Song Events Original
  • Song Patterns
  • Song Events
  • Empty
  • Song Number Original
  • Song Number Current

See Also:
EsxPackage.getSong()
